        "body": "This patch fixes an issue with the calculation of coverage percentage for badges. The\r\nissue is that all badges were being generated with a `0%` percentage on\r\nthem, no matter the coverage. This was due to an integer division that\r\nalways resulted in zero. Doing a floating-point division instead solves\r\nit.\r\n\r\nCloses #763",
